{
  "stem": "5516.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, we had a uniform.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Green.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, they used to give badges, too.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know if I had a badge [? this time. ?]",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it was quite a few.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I do not remember how many, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If I would tell you, I have to just guess it, you know?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, we had quite a few, you know, from Jewish kids, you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had a-- we used to always-- together, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And we used to spend time a lot in school, too, you know, in spare time and this.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I, I, I wasn't in this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "One time, they took me in a play where I didn't do nothing there, like a storekeeper.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They made like a little store, you know?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They was on the stage, and I like a-- like a storekeeper.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH SPEECH]-- I, I have no idea because when I grew up, I didn't have my grandparents.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Uncles-- we had uncles in a different state, next to it, Latvia, if you heard.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You heard Latvia.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There used to be a city, Dvinsk, because before the war, my father was in this city.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My father married in, in Dvinsk.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "His wife is from Dvinsk.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he was living in Dvinsk.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "See.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] Since the uncles-- all of them was there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it's-- years ago, when you used to go from one country to another one, you had to have a passport, like you go from here.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was difficult, you know?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Well, my father used to go once in a while.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Once in a year, I think, he used to go to his rabbi, you know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "See, like in United State, they got a rabbi, you know, where they-- he's leader, you know.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
